HEADWORD: Blanketing
<hw>Blan"ket*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Cloth for
blankets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or punishment of tossing in a
