[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That affair of the <qex>blanketing</qex> happened to thee for the
fault thou wast guilty of.</q> <rj><qau>Smollett.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

